rows.label: tev013702_MSG0001
rows.name:
Are you familiar with the xenoform named Professor B
who lives on the outskirts of the industrial district?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev013702_MSG0002
rows.name: Who is he? Do you have any idea what he's doing?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev013702_MSG0003
rows.name:
I mean, he buys lots of parts from me,
and I'm grateful to have him as a customer...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev013702_MSG0004
rows.name:
But his orders have left me baffled as to what he's
trying to build. And when I ask about his work,
I end up more confused than when I started.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev013702_MSG0005
rows.name:
There's just so much I don't understand, and it makes
me a little uneasy... Like, when exactly did he even
start living here in New LA?[ST:wait ]
